A Cape Town man, who used to live on the streets for many years, is helping those who are still homeless. He’s launched the Homeless Hub, inspired by his personal experiences. Tanya Nefdt has more #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - A Cape Town man, who used to live on the streets for many years, is helping those who are still homeless. He has launched the Homeless Hub, inspired by his personal experiences. READ: Cape Town’s homeless | WATCH | Plight of people living on the street Its aim is to help people start over by empowering them with new skills. On offer is training in business, management and even sewing. Watch the video above for more details on this story.